### NduthiRide — Chat endpoints (REST fallback)
### Real-time messaging is via WebSocket (/chat namespace).
### These REST endpoints serve as fallback for message history and management.
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@userToken = <paste_user_access_token_here>
@riderToken = <paste_rider_access_token_here>
@rideId = <paste_ride_id_here>
@parcelId = <paste_parcel_id_here>
@conversationId = <paste_conversation_id_here>
@messageId = <paste_message_id_here>

### ─── Get conversation for a ride (with last 30 messages) ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversation/ride/{{rideId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Get conversation for a parcel delivery ─────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversation/parcel/{{parcelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Fetch paginated message history (cursor-based) ────────
### First page — no cursor
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages?conversationId={{conversationId}}&limit=30
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Load older messages — pass the nextCursor from the previous response
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages?conversationId={{conversationId}}&cursor={{messageId}}&limit=30
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Send a text message (REST fallback) ────────────────────
### Prefer WebSocket chat:send event for real-time delivery
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages?conversationId={{conversationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "I am 5 minutes away!",
  "type": "TEXT"
}

### ─── Send a location pin ─────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages?conversationId={{conversationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{riderToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "My current location",
  "type": "LOCATION",
  "locationPin": {
    "lat": -1.2921,
    "lng": 36.8219,
    "address": "Nairobi CBD, Kenyatta Avenue"
  }
}

### ─── Soft-delete own message (within 5 minutes of sending) ──
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages/{{messageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###
### ─── WebSocket events reference ──────────────────────────────
### Connect to: ws://localhost:3000/chat
### Auth:        socket.handshake.auth = { token: "<accessToken>" }
###
### Client → Server:
###   chat:join    { conversationId }
###   chat:leave   { conversationId }
###   chat:send    { conversationId, content, type?, locationPin? }
###   chat:typing  { conversationId, isTyping: true|false }
###   chat:read    { conversationId }
###
### Server → Client:
###   chat:joined       { conversationId }
###   chat:message      { id, conversationId, content, type, senderRole, senderName, createdAt, ... }
###   chat:typing       { senderAccountId, isTyping }
###   chat:read-receipt { readBy, readAt }
###   chat:closed       { conversationId, closedAt }
